data.description: GREAT 2 BEDROOM 1 BATH HOME ON DEAD END STREET. BOTH BEDROOMS HAVE CEDAR CLOSETS WITH EXTRA STORAGE CABINETS ABOVE. LARGE WOODED AND FENCED BACK YARD WITH FIREPIT AND 12X18 PATIO. UPDATED BATH (to studs) '23, KITCHEN '09, ALL NEW WINDOWS '09, FURNACE '09, FAMILY ROOM ADDITION '11, WATER HEATER '12.
